d":"ce0ca020865bfdfa03f810f6b62afaeac9b3a591","tid":1309493,"uid":175629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:22:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f773f27f429ae2003b74e8d60c6a8f8ade170c7","tid":1309493,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"944a7ed9cd9d74a0ffea55dc2c15246c454a94a4","tid":1309493,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:39:01.000Z","msg":"遊行前後都記得幫襯下上水既吉野家啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n==============================<br />\n幫襯流程如下:<br />\n<ins><strong>你</strong></ins><br />\n我想要一個特大牛肉飯 加大 走牛肉<br />\n少飯多汁加酸薑<br />\n汽水走冰少甜外賣杯上<br />\n另加吉列豬扒飯走飯 豬扒免炸走肥<br />\n飯要炒飯底走汁走青<br />\n飲麵豉湯少鹹<br />\n全部外賣唔要餐具<br />\n唔該覆一次單?<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>收銀</strong></ins><br />\n...................<br />\n...................<br />\n盛惠 73.5<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>你</strong></ins><br />\n(搵銀包搵錢搵1分鐘)<br />\n唔好意思 無帶錢<br />\n都係唔要喇 淨係比杯水我丫<br />\n唔該哂<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>收銀</strong></ins><br />\n...................<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>你</strong></ins><br />\n想要包酸薑tim 唔該哂<br />\n<br />\n==================================<br />\n跟住飲水食酸薑坐到體力充足再出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:24:45.000Z","msg":"屌你老母搞著前線啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n企喺門口冇客入唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e2054a0242752eb1cf6e02851a5b1734bc051f","tid":1309493,"uid":8532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:25:03.000Z","msg":"急呀"}]}